name: No Rate Limit
description: Prevents you from getting rate-limited by Robtop's API

maxReqs.name: Max Requests per Minute
maxReqs.description: The maximum amount of requests you can make to Robtop's API per minute (you get banned at 100)

maxDownloadLevelReqs.name: Max Level Download Requests per Minute
maxDownloadLevelReqs.description: The maximum amount of level download requests you can make to Robtop's API per minute (you get banned at 20)
